OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy fog will soon clear
OL,6,Fthen another dry day with long periods
OL,7,Fof sunshine. Becoming warm inland by
OL,8,Fthe afternoon but cooler near the
OL,9,Fcoast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some evening
OL,12,Fsunshine to start with. Clear spells
OL,13,Fallow patchy fog or frost to develop
OL,14,Fin west overnight, while low cloud and
OL,15,Fmist gradually return to the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
