OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAny overnight mist or fog
OL,6,Flifting through the morning. Staying
OL,7,Fdry but much cooler with variable
OL,8,Fcloud in the east. Still warm with
OL,9,Fprolonged spells of sunshine in the
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,13,Fspells and variable cloud on Sunday
OL,14,Fand Monday with the chance of a few
OL,15,Fshowers. Mostly dry Tuesday but cool
OL,16,Fand cloudy in east, warmer and sunnier
OL,17,Fin west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
